::{{A|VO Side1 hk3 auctioneerA 110.ogg}} '''Auction Staff:''' Then there's the standard auction procedure. The auctioneer presents the items, and the bidders place their bids on the spot... Pretty straightforward, don't you think?
:;(Return to previous option selection)
