::{{A|VO Side1 hk3 auctioneerA 112.ogg}} '''Auction Staff:''' There are lots of prospectors hunting for ancient relics in the vagrant camp, so there should be a lot of unique items at this auction. For example, I heard that one of the goods up for auction is a barely used Geomarrow Probe...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Geomarrow Probe?
::{{A|VO Side1 hk3 auctioneerA 113.ogg}} '''Auction Staff:''' Ah, never heard of a treasure like that before, huh? More excited about the auction now?
::{{A|VO Side1 hk3 auctioneerA 114.ogg}} '''Auction Staff:''' Oh, here &mdash; take this pamphlet. It has more information on all the rarities up for auction. Remember to stop by the vagrant camp! Be there or be square!
{{Dialogue End}}

