:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Kids today like things that are a little more "extreme"...
::{{A|VO Side1 hk3 hook 145.ogg}} '''Hook:''' Huh? Y&mdash;Yeah, that's right! Hook spotted loads of cool stuff at the auction!
::{{A|VO Side1 hk3 hook 146.ogg}} '''Hook:''' For example, there's this teddy bear called Junjun! Your niece will love him!
